```console
pip install tailwindall
```

> [!IMPORTANT]
> A python all in one package for doing everything, including:
> - Graphing
> - UI
> - Website development
> - Statistics
> - Maths
>   - Shape identification
>   - Angle calculation
> - And more!


> [!NOTE] 
